hadiths[56]{hadithnumber,text}:
2788,Hazrat Mikhnaf bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Arafat mein waquf kiye huey they ke aapney farmaya : ''logo! be-shak her ghar walon par her saal qurbani hai aur Ateera. kya jantey ho ke Ateera kya hai? yehi jisey log ( رجبية ( kehtey hain. '' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Ateera (yani ( رجبية ( ) mansookh hai aur ye hadees mansookh hai.
2789,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Azha ke din ke mutalliq hukm diya gaya hai ke usey bator eid manun jissey ke Allah azz-w-jall ne is ummat ke liye khas kya hai.'' eik aadmi ne kaha : farmaiye ke agar mujhey doodh ke janwer ke siwa koi janwer na miley to kya main uski qurbani kar dun? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, balke apney baal kaat lo, nakhun aur munchhein tarash lo aur zere-naaf ki safai kar lo. Allah ke yahan tumhari yehi kamil qurbani hogi.''"
2790,"Janab Hanash (Kinani, sanaani) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo do mendhon ki qurbani kya kartey they. maine un se puchha : ye kya hai? to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey wasiyat farmaai thi ke main unki taraf se qurbani kya karun. chunanche main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se qurbani kya karta hun."
2791,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiskey paas koi janwar ho jisey wo ( qurbani ke liye ( zibeh karna chahta ho to zul-hijja ka chaand nazar aa janey ke baad apney baal aur nakhun hergiz na kaatey yahan tak ke qurbani kar ley. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Imam Malik aur Muhammad bin Amr ke talaamiza ka ''Amr bin Muslim'' ke naam mein ikhtilaf hai. kuchh usey umr bin Muslim kehtey hain jabkey aksar ne Amr kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ye Amr bin Muslim bin Ukaima Laisi Al Jundai hai.
2792,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya, eik mendhaa laya jaey jo seengon wala ho, paon kalay hon, aankhen kaali hon, seena aur pet bhi kaalaa ho, chunanche wo pesh kiya gaya to aapney usey qurban kiya. aapney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! chhuri lao.'' phir farmaya : ''isey pathar par tez karo.'' maine aisey hi kiya, phir aapney chhuri li aur mendhey ko pakda, usey litaya aur zibeh kiya aur dua ki : (باسم اللہ ، اللهم ! تقبل من محمد وآل محمد ومن أمة محمد) ''aey Allah Muhammad , aale Muhammad aur ummate Muhammad ki taraf se qubul farma.'' phir usey qurban (zibeh) kar diya."
2793,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saat oontniyaan apney haath se khadi haalat mein nahar (qurban) kin . aur Madina munawwara mein aapney do mendhey qurban kiye jo seengon waley aur chitkabrey they.
2794,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do mendhey zibeh kiye jo seengon waley aur chitkabrey they. zibeh kartey huey aapney takbir padhi aur (بسم الله) kaha : (بسم الله والله اكبر ( , aur apna paon unki gardan par rakha."
2795,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din do mendhey zibeh kiye jo seengon waley, chitkabrey aur khassi they. jab aapney unhen qibla rukh kya to ye dua padhi : (إني وجهت وجهي للذي فطر السموات والأرض على ملة إبراهيم حنيفا وما أنا من المشركين ، إن صلاتي ونسكي ومحياي ومماتي لله رب العالمين لا شريك له وبذلك أمرت وأنا من المسلمين ، اللهم منك ولك an محمد وأمته باسم الله والله أكبر) ''maine apna rukh us zaat ki taraf kar liya jisney aasmano aur zameen ko paida kiya hai, main millate Ibrahim par hun aur yak-su hun, aur mushrikon mein se nahin hun, bila-shuba meri Namaz , meri qurbani , mera jeena aur mera marna Allah hi ke liye hai jo tamam jahan walon ka paalney wala hai, uska koi shareek nahin, mujhey isi baat ka hukm diya gaya hai aur main itaat guzaaron mein se hun, aey Allah ! ye (qurbani) teri taraf se hai aur terey hi liye hai, isey Muhammad aur iski ummat ki taraf se qubul farma, Allah ke naam se aur Allah sab se bada hai.'' phir aapney usey zibeh kar diya."
2796,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisa mendhaa qurbani kya kartey they jo seengon wala aur nar (ghair khassi) hota, jo siyahi mein dekhta (aankhen siyah hotin) , siyahi mein khata (munh kaalaa hota) aur siyahi mein chalta tha (paon bhi kalay hotey)."
2797,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf do daanta janwer hi zibeh karo, siwaye uskey ke tumharey liye bahut mushkil ho jaey to bhed ka do sala bachcha zibeh kar saktey ho.''"
2798,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba mein qurbaaniyaan taqseem farmaen to mujhey bakri ka eik bachcha inayat farmaya jo jazaa tha. mein usey lekar aap ki khidmat mein aaya aur arz kiya : ye to jazaa hai, aapney farmaya : ''isey hi qurban kar do.'' chunanche maine uski qurbani kar di."
2799,Janab Aasim bin Kulaib apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi ke sath they jin ka naam Mujaashea' tha jo ke qabeela bani Sulaim mein se they. (qurbani ke liye) bakriyan (taqseem ki gaeen to) kam ho gaeen. isliye unhoney eik manadi kerney waley ko hukm diya ke wo aelan kar dey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''bila-shuba (جذع) (eik saala) (ثني) (do daante) ki jagah kifaayat kar jata hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : us (sahabi) ka naam Mujaashea' bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hai.
2800,"Hazrat Bara (bin Aazib) (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke roz Namaz ke baad khutba diya aur farmaya : ''jisney hamari tarah Namaz padhi aur hamari tarah qurbani ki uski qurbani sahih hui aur jisney Namaz se pehley qurbani ki to wo gosht ki bakri hai. '' Abu-Barda bin Niyaar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur boley : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qasam ! maine Namaz ke liye aaney se pehley hi qurbani kar di, maine samjha ke aaj ka din khaney peeney ka din hai to maine jaldi ki, khud bhi khaya aur apney ghar walon aur hamsaayon (padosiyon) ko bhi khilaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to gosht ki bakri hui.'' phir usney kaha : merey paas bakri ka bachcha hai jo jazaa (eik saala) hai aur ye gosht ki do bakriyon se bhi badh kar hai to kya ye meri taraf se kafi hogi? aapney farmaya : ''haan, lekin terey baad kisi ke liye hergiz kafi nahin hogi.''"
2801,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey mamu ne jin ka naam Abu-Barda tha, Namaz se pehley hi qurbani kar dali. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''teri bakri to gosht ki bakri hui.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas ghar ki pali hui eik jazaa bakri hai. aapney farmaya : ''usey zibeh kar do, lekin terey siwa kisi aur ke liye durust nahin hogi.''"
2802,"Janab Ubaid bin Fairoz kehtey hain, maine Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya ke qurbani mein kon sa janwer jayez nahin? to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein khutba deney ke liye khadey huey . ... . aur meri ungliyan aur porey aap ki ungliyon aur poron se bahut hech hain. ... aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (chaar ungliyon ke ishara sey) farmaya : ''chaar qism ke janwar qurbani mein jayez nahin hain, kaanaa jis ka kaanaa pan zahir ho, bimar jiski bimari wazeh ho, langda jis ka langda-pan zahir ho aur intehai kamzor ke uski haddi mein goodaa na ho.'' main (Ubaid bin Fairoz) ne kaha : mujhey aisa janwar bhi napasand hai jiskey daant mein aeb ho, Hazrat Bara ne kaha : jo tumhen napasand ho to usey chhod do magar doosron ke liye haram na thehrao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : (la tanqee) ke maani hain jis (ki haddiyon) mein goodaa na ho. (bilkul laaghir, haddiyon ka dhaancha ho.)"
2803,"Yazid Zoo Misr bayan kartey hain ke main Utba bin Abd Salma ke paas aaya aur (us sey) kaha : aey Abul-Waleed ! main qurbani leney ke liye nikla hun magar koi janwar pasand nahin aaya siwaye eik ke, ke uskey daant gir gaey hain. magar wo bhi mujhey pasand nahin hai to aap iskey baarey mein kya kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : wo tum ne mujhey kyon nahin la diya. maine kaha : Subhanallah ! tumhari taraf se jayez hoga to kya merey taraf se jayez na hoga? unhoney kaha : haan (is liye ke) tum shak kartey ho aur mujhey koi shak nahin hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un janwaron se mana kiya hai jo (مصفرة ، مستأصلة ، بخقاء ، مشيعة) ya (كسراء) hon. (مصفرة) : wo hai jis ka kaan jad se kat gaya ho ke uska surakh nazar aaney lagey, (مستأصلة) : wo hai jis ka seeng jad se nikal gaya ho, (بخقاء) : wo hai jiski beenai jati rahey magar aankh qaaim ho, (مشيعة) : wo hai jo naatawaani aur kamzori ki wajeh se dusri bakriyon ke sath na chal sakey aur (كسراء) : wo hai jiski taang toot gaee ho."
2804,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham (qurbani ke janwaron ki) aankhen aur kaan ghaur se dekh liya keren aur koi aisi qurbani na keren jo kaani ho ya uska kaan aagey ya peechey se kataa hua ho ya kaan chira hua ho ya us mein surakh ho. Zaheer kehtey hain : maine Abu-Is'haq se puchha : kya azbaa (seeng tooti) ka bhi zikr kiya tha? unhoney kaha : nahin. maine kaha : مقابلة se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : jiskey kaan ka kinaaraa kataa hua ho. maine kaha : مدابرة kya hai : kaha : jis ka kaan peechhey ki taraf se kataa hua ho. maine puchha ke شرقاء kisey kehtey hain? kaha : jis ka kaan chira hua ho. maine kaha : خرقاء kisey kehtey hain : kaha ke jiskey kaan mein alamat ke taur par surakh kar diya gaya ho."
2805,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisi qurbani kerney se mana farmaya hai jis ka kaan ya seeng jad se kat gaya ho ya toot gaya ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Jari bin Kulaib, sadoosi hai, Basra ka rehney wala hai is se Qatada ke siwa aur kisi ne hadees nahin li."
2806,Janab Qatada kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se puchha ke (أعضب) kisey kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : aisa janwar jis ka seeng aadha ya us se ziyada tootaa hua ho.
2807,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein (hajj) tamatto kartey they, saat afrad ki taraf se eik gaey zibeh kartey they aur ham sab is mein shareek ho jatey they."
2808,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gaey saat afrad ki taraf se hai aur oont bhi saat afrad ki taraf se hai.''"
2809,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Hudebiya mein oont saat afrad ki taraf se nahar kuiya aur gaey saat afrad ki taraf se zibeh ki.
2810,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke main eik eidul-azhaa ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eid gaah mein hazir tha. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna khutba mukammal kar liya aur member se utrey to aap ko eik mendhaa pesh kiya gaya. aapney usey apney haath se zibeh kiya aur ye dua padhi : (بسم الله والله أكبر هذا عني وعمن لم يضح من أمتي) ''Allah ke naam sey, aur Allah sab se bada hai, ye meri taraf se aur meri ummat ke un logon ki taraf se hai jo qurbani nahin kar sakey.''"
2811,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni qurbani eid-gaah hi mein zibeh kiya kartey they aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bhi yehi amal tha.
2812,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein (eik baar) eid-ul-azhaa ke moqe par dehaaton ke log bahut ziyada aagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni qurbaniyon mein se teen raat ke liye rakh lo aur baqi sadqa kar do.'' bayan karti hain ke phir uskey baad ka moqa aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! log (pehley) apni qurbaniyon se faeyda uthatey they, unki charbi jama kar letey they aur un (ki khaalon) se mishkeezey bana letey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to (ab) kya hua?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney qurbani ka gosht teen raat se ziyada rakhney se mana farma diya hai. aapney farmaya : ''maine tumhen is wajeh se roka tha ke tumharey paas dehati log bahut ziyada aagey they. so tum khao, sadqa karo aur rakh bhi lo.''"
2813,"Hazrat Nabeesha Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham ne tum logon ko qurbaniyon ka gosht teen din se ziyada rakhney se isliye mana kiya tha ke tum sab ko gosht pahunch jaey aur (ab) Allah taala ne tumhen wusat de-di hai (aur ghani kar diya hai) isliye khaao, zakhira karo aur ajr kamaaoo, khabrdar ! ye din khaney peeney aur Allah ke zikr karney ke din hain.''"
2814,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke do baaten maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hain : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne har cheez ke sath ehsan ko wajib kiya hai, so jab tum qatl karo to us mein bhi ehsan karo.'' Muslim bin Ibrahim ke siwa kisi doosrey raawi ke alfaz hain : (فأحسنوا القتلة) ''isliye achhai ke sath qatl karo. aur jab zibeh karo to achhi tarah zibeh karo. chahiye ke zibeh kerney wala apni chhuri ko tez kar ley aur apney janwar ko rahat pahunchaey.''"
2815,"Hisham bin Zaid kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Hakam bin Ayub ke paas gaya, unhoney dekha ke kuchh naujawan ya ladkey eik murghi ko khada karkey us par nishana maar rahey hain. to Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke janwaron ko baandha jaey (aur qatl kiya jaey)."
2816,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ki phir farmaya : ''aey Soban ! hamarey liye is bakri ka gosht banao.'' kehtey hain : phir main aap ko us se khilata raha yahan tak ke ham Madiney aagey.
2817,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Allah ka farman hai : (فكلوا مما ذكر اسم الله عليه) ''khaao wo chizen jin par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho.'' aur agli aayat mein hai : (ولا تأكلوا مما لم يذكر اسم الله عليه) ''wo chizen mat khao jin par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho.'' isey mansookh karkey (ehle-kitab ke tuaam (khaane) ko hamarey liye halal kar diya gaya aur) farmaya :(وطعام الذين أوتوا الكتاب حل لكم وطعامكم حل لهم) ''jin logon ko kitab di gaee hai unka tuaam (khaana) tumharey liye halal hai aur tumhara tuaam unke liye halal hai.''
2818,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se Allah taala ke farman : (وإن الشياطين ليوحون إلى أوليائهم) ''aur shaitan apney doston ko ilhaam kartey hain.'' (ki tafseer) mein marwi (bayan) hai ke wo kehtey hain : jisey Allah ne zibeh kiya (maara) ho usey mat khao aur jisey tum khud zibeh karo, wo kha lo. tu Allah taala ne nazil farmaya : (ولا تأكلوا مما لم يذكر اسم الله عليه) ''wo chiz mat khao jis par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho.''"
2819,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke yahudi log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : ham wo to kha letey hain jo khud qatl kartey hain aur jisey Allah ne qatl kiya (maara) ho usey nahin khatey? tu Allah taala ne nazil farmaya : (ولا تأكلوا مما لم يذكر اسم الله عليه) ''aur jis par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho usey mat khao . ... .''
2820,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne arab ke badduon ke is amal se mana farmaya hai jis mein wo muqabley bazi mein oont zibeh kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Ghandar ne is riwayat ko Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) par mauquf kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : (raawi hadees) Abu-Raihana ka naam Abdullah bin matar hai."
2821,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kal ham dushman se milen gey lekin hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahin hain, to kya ham pathar se ya lathi ke tez phatey se zibeh kar saktey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phurti dikha, ya jaldi kar, jo chiz bhi khoon baha dey aur us par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho to usey khao, lekin daant ya nakhun na ho, main tumhen uskey mutalliq batata hun ke daant haddi hai aur nakhun Habshi logon ki chhuri hai.'' aur kuchh jald baaz log aagey badhey aur unhoney jaldi ki, unhen kuchh ghaneematen mil gaee thin jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ke peechhey they, unhoney degchey aag par rakh diye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un degchiyon ke paas se guzrey to aapney hukm diya aur unhen ulat diya gaya aur un mein (ghaneematen) taqseem ki, to eik oont ko das bakriyon ke barabar kiya. aur jamaat ke oonton mein se eik oont bhag khada hua, unke paas ghodey nahin they, to eik aadmi ne usko teer maara aur Allah ne usko rok liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''in janwaron mein bhi bidak kar bhagney waley hotey hain jaisey ke deegar wehshi (jangli janwer), to jo in mein se is tarah se karey, uskey sath isi tarah karo.''"
2822,"Muhammad bin Safwan ya Safwan bin Muhammad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : maine do khargosh shikar kiye to maine unko pathar se zibeh kiya. phir maine unke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney mujhey unke khaney ka hukm diya."
2823,"Banu Harisa ke eik shakhs se riwayat hai ke wo uhud ki eik ghaati mein doodh deney wali oontni charaaya karta tha. to us oontni ko maut ne aa liya aur usey koi chiz na mili jis se wo usey nahar karta. phir usney eik meekh (khunti) li aur usey uskey labbey (narkharaa, seeney ke paas nahar kerney ki jagah) mein ghonp diya yahan tak ke uska khoon beh gaya. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur iskey mutalliq sab kuchh bataya, to aapney iskey khaney ka hukm diya."
2824,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaiye ke ham mein se koi shikar karta hai aur uskey paas chhuri nahin hoti to kya wo isey pathar se ya lakdi ke tez phatey se zibeh kar ley? aapney farmaya : ''khoon bahao, jis se bhi tum chaho aur Allah ka naam zikr karo.''"
2825,"Janab Abu Ushraa apney walid se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool : kya janwar ka zibeh karna labbey (narkharey) se ya halaq hi se hota hai? aapney farmaya : ''agar to uski raan mein bhi koi teer waghaira maar dey to kafi hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye soorat sirf us janwar mein hai jo kahin nichey ja gira ho ya wehshi bin gaya ho."
2826,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shaitan ke zabiha se mana farmaya hai. Imam ibne Esa ne apni hadees mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai (shaitan ke zabiha se murad ye hai ke) zabiha ki khaal kaat di jaey magar ragein na kaati jaeyn aur phir usey yunhi chhod diya jaey yahan tak ke mar jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Amr bin Abdullah ko Amr Barq kaha jata hai, Ikrima uskey walid ke yahan Yamen mein mehman thehrey they. aur Maamer jab is se riwayat kartey hain to wo Amr bin Abdullah kehtey hain aur jab ehale Yamen riwayat kartey hain to iska naam zikr nahin kartey."
2827,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se pet ke bachchey ke mutalliq sawal kiya, to aapney farmaya : ''agar chaho to kha lo.'' Musaddad ke alfaz mein yun hai ke ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham koi oontni, gaey ya bakri zibeh kartey hain to uskey pet se bachcha nikal aata hai, kya ham usey kha lein ya phenk den? aapney farmaya : ''agar chaho to kha lo. bila-shuba uski maa ka zibeh karna hi uskey liye zibeh hai.''"
2828,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bachchey ka zibeh karna uski maa ke zibeh karney mein hai.''
2829,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kuchh log, jo jahiliyat se naey naey nikley hain, hamarey paas gosht latey hain, hamein maloom nahin hota ke unhoney in janweron ko zibeh kartey huey ''(بسم الله)'' padhi ya nahin, to kya ham ye kha lein? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Allah ka naam lo aur kha lo.''"
2830,"Hazrat Nubaisa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pukar kar kaha : ham jahiliyat mein rajab ke mahiney mein qurbani kiya kartey they. (Ateera) to aap hamein kya irshad farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ke liye zibeh karo jis mahiney mein bhi ho, Shan Wale Allah ke liye neki karo aur khilaya karo.'' us aadmi ne kaha ke ham jahiliyat mein faraa' bhi kartey they, to aap hamein kya farmatey hain? farmaya : ''tamam charney waley janwaron main eik faraa' hai (zabiha hai) ye naya paida hua bachcha jisey ki terey doosrey janwar ghiza detey hain yahan tak ke jab wo bojh uthaney ke qabil ho jaey.'' Nasr bin Ali ne kaha : ''jab wo hajiyon ko uthaney ke qabil ho jaey to to usey zibeh kar aur uska gosht sadqa kar. Khalid Hazza kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke (Ustad Abu-Qulaba ne) yun kaha : ''musafiron par sadqa kar bila-shuba ye khair ka amal hai.'' Khalid Hazza kehtey hain : maine Ustad Abu-Qulaba se puchha ke saayema (charney waley) janwaron ki tadaad kya hoti hai? unhoney kaha : eik sau."
2831,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na (faraa') (wajib) hai aur na (عتيرة).''
2832,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai : ''(faraa')'' us bachchey ko kehtey they jo unke janwaron mein sab se pehley paida hota, phir wo usey zibeh kar detey they."
2833,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke her pachas bakriyon main eik bakri (sadqa) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : baaz ulama ne bayan kiya hai ke ''faraa' '' se murad oonton mein paida honey wala pehla bachcha hota tha jisey wo log apney buton ke naam se zibeh kartey they, gosht kha letey aur uska chamdaa kisi darkht par dal detey they. aur ''عتيرة'' usey kehtey they jisey wo rajab ke pehley das dino mein zibeh kartey they."
2834,"Hazrat Umme-kurz Ka'biya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan barabar barabar (eik jaisi) aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se suna, kehtey they ke (مكافئتان) ke maani hain ke dono bakriyan barabar barabar hon ya qarib qarib hon."
2835,"Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''parindon ko apney ghoslon mein rehney do. (unhen achcha ya bura shagoon leney ke liye na udao) kehti hain : aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, farmatey they : ''ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan hon aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri , aur koi harj nahin ke dono muzakkir hon ya dono muannas.''"
2836,Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan hain ham misl (eik jaisi) aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : sahih hadees yehi hai jabkey Sufiyan ki hadees weham hai.
2837,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her bachcha apney aqeeqe ke sath girwi hota hai. (lihaza) saatwen din uski taraf se janwar zibeh kiya jaey, sar mundaayaa jaey aur us par khoon lagaya jaey.'' Qatada (Rahimahullah) se jab ye puchha jata ke khoon kis tarah lagaya jaey to kehtey : jab janwar zibeh kiya ja raha ho to uskey chand baal lekar uski (katney wali) ragon ke aagey kar do aur bachchey ki chundiya par rakh diye jaeyn yahan tak ke wo (taza-taza khoon) uskey sar par dhaagey ki manind bahney lagey. phir uska sar dhoya jaey aur baal moond diye jaeyn. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (ويدمى) khoon laganey wali baat Hammam ka weham hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is jumley mein Hammam ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai. deegar log (ويسمى) riwayat kartey hain (bachchey ka naam rakha jaey) magar Hammam ne us lafz ko (يدمى) keh diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ye qabile amal bhi nahin hai."
2838,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har bachcha apney aqeeqe ke sath girwi hota hai (lihaza) saatwen din uski taraf se janwar zibeh kiya jaey, uska sar munda jaey aur naam rakha jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : lafz (يسمى) sahih tar hai. Salam bin Abi Mutee ne Qatada se aur Ayas bin Daghfal aur Ash'as ne ba-waaste Hasan lafz : (ويسمى) riwayat kiya hai aur Ash'as ne Hasan se, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi lafz : (ويسمى) bayan kiya hai."
2839,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir Zabi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladkey ke liye  Aqeeqa lazimi hai, lihaza uski taraf se khoon bahao aur uska mail kuchail door karo.''"
2840,Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey they ke (إماطة الأذى) (mail kuchail door kerney) se murad bachchey ka sar mundna hai.
2841,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke Aqeeqe main eik eik mendhaa zibeh kiya tha.
2842,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur mera khayal hai ke wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Aqeeqe ke baarey mein puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''Jalal Wala Allah ''(uqooq)'' ko pasand nahin farmata , goya aapney ( Aqeeqeعقیقہ ka ( naam pasand nahin farmaya. (kyonkey Aqeeqe aur uqooq ka mada eik hai) aapney farmaya : ''jis ke yahan bachchey ki wiladat ho aur wo uski taraf se sadqa aur qurbani karna chahta ho to karey, ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan barabar barabar . aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, (faraa') ke mutalliq puchha gaya , to aapney farmaya : ''faraa' bhi haq hai aur chahiye ke us (nau-zaayeda) janwar ko chhod do , yahan tak ke jab wo eik saal ka ya do saal ka khoob mota-taaza ho jaey to kisi bewa ko dey do ya jihad fi-sabee-lil-lah Allah main (sawari ke liye) dey do , ye behtar hai us se ke tum usey zibeh kar dalo jabkey uska gosht uskey baalon hi se laga hua ho, aur apney bartan ko tum ondha kar dalo aur apni oontni ko be-qarar aur be-chain kar chhodo.''"
2843,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida kehtey hain : maine apney walid Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke daure jahiliyat mein jab ham mein se kisi ke yahan bachchey ki wiladat hoti to wo eik bakri zibeh karta aur uska khoon bachchey ke sar par chipad deta tha aur jab se Allah ne hamein Islam ki nemat se nawaza hai to ham eik bakri zibeh kartey hain, bachchey ka sar moondtey hain aur uskey sar par Zaafran mal detey hain."
